Resource Profile: MedicationDispense: Original

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/MedicationDispenseOriginal Version: 1.5.30
Active as of 2025-05-25 Computable Name: MedicationDispenseOriginal

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for VistA file PRESCRIPTION (52) to MedicationDispense.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.

Use Case Overview

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: Debt Portal ChargeItem[charges]
  • CapabilityStatements using this Resource Profile: AMPL GUI and Lung Cancer Screening
